ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectCEFTA Rules of Origin for Casual Goods Regulations
PrecisCanada-European Free Trade Association Free Trade Agreement (CEFTA) Rules of Origin for Casual Goods Regulations set out the origin requirements for low-value shipments and for goods imported by travelers to ensure that eligible goods qualify without onerous documentation requirements.
